Field Detail

ButtonBarContainerTheme

public static final int[] ButtonBarContainerTheme
Declare custom theme attributes that allow changing which styles are used for button bars depending on the API level. ?android:attr/buttonBarStyle is new as of API 11 so this is necessary to support previous API levels.

Includes the following attributes:

AttributeDescription
com.example.musicplayer:buttonBarButtonStyle
com.example.musicplayer:buttonBarStyle

See Also:
ButtonBarContainerTheme_buttonBarButtonStyle, ButtonBarContainerTheme_buttonBarStyle

ButtonBarContainerTheme_buttonBarButtonStyle

public static final int ButtonBarContainerTheme_buttonBarButtonStyle

This symbol is the offset where the R.attr.buttonBarButtonStyle attribute's value can be found in the ButtonBarContainerTheme array.

Must be a reference to another resource, in the form "@[+][package:]type:name" or to a theme attribute in the form "?[package:][type:]name".
